      • hitMonster

        public boolean hitMonster(java.util.ArrayList<Monster> monsters)
        Returns whether or not the Projectile has hit a Monster. This also handles the health subtraction of the Monster.
        Parameters:
        monsters - List of monsters the Projectile may hit
        Returns:
        True if at least one monster is hit, false if otherwise.
        Postconditions:
        This method subtracts health from hit Monsters.
